verbose_text: The changes of TRE activity were not only consistent with the changes of the transcripts of Ab-tre, but also Ab-tps1 and Ab-tps2 which might account for the indistinctive changes of trehalose; however the level of trehalose still declined as long as the transcript of Ab-tre and TRE activity increased which indicated that trehalose might be more likely to be effective by being hydrolyzed, and this also testified that TRE and trehalose should play a role in coping with hypertonic dehydration.
